Analysis data Valorant Championship Tour Asian Pacific (VCT APAC) 2023¶

Data Introduction¶

In this project I will do a simple analysis to see the factors that influence players, see the best performance of each variable in contributing to a match and overall statistics in the team.

I got this data from https://www.vlr.gg/stats and I took it from the APAC (Asian Pacific) region of the 2023 league.

Information about variables :¶

  • RND = Rounds Played
  • R = Rating
  • ACS = Average Combat Score
  • K:D = Kill : Death
  • KAST = Kill, Assist, Trade, Survive
  • ADR = Average Damage per Round
  • KPR = Kills per Round
  • APR = Assist per Round
  • FKPR = First Kill per Round
  • FDPR = First Death per Round
  • HS% = Headshot
  • CL% = Clutch Success
  • CL(won/Played)
  • KMAX = Maximum Kills in a Single Map
  • FK = First Kill
  • FD = First Death
  • K,D,A = Kill, Death, Assist

# formating #

## extract data win and played to separate column ##
vctApac[['CW', 'PLY']] = vctApac['CL'].str.extract(r'^(\d).*(\d{2})$') 
# r untuk membuat raw string
# ^(\d) untuk mengambil angka atau karakter pertama
# .* untuk menangani karakter yang ada di tengah
# (\d{2})$ untuk mengambil dua angka atau karakter terakhir
# delete unneeded column

## delete uneeded column ##
# using function drop() with parameter axis for get the colum not the row
vctApac = vctApac.drop(['CL', 'Unnamed: 18'], axis= 1)

KAST-A Insight¶

KAST is stands for Kills, Assist, Survive, Trade. This meaning the player who got kills, helping their teammate, survive until the end of the game, and being traded by a teammate within a short time after dying.

In short KAST is the player who can get succesfully survive and kills to help their teammate.

In that scatterplot we can see d4v41 got the highest KAST percentage.

According to https://gametree.me/gaming-terms/valorant/kast/ KAST is calculated by KAST % = (Rounds with a Kill, Assist, Survival, or Trade / Total Rounds Played) x 100

CL% Insight¶

Clutch (CL) is the player who can win a round when being a last man standing. Clutch also have a strong correlation with kills (K). but even the player have the most kills it dosen't mean the player got the win clutch in a round.

As we can see something is the most player who have the highest Clutch Percentage. This meaning that the player have most won a round they played when this player being the last man standing. This statistics is depens on your round you played and how much you can win.

If we look of the agent player used, most of the agent is controller. The controller agent have the abillity to cut a vision a enemy and taking control of an area, and forcing the enemy into choke points.

Team Insight¶

Over all PRX and GE being the team that have a good statistics among other team, this indicates how the individually player in the team have a good skills and good comps. It's not just about individual skills and agent composition, there are non-technical factors that can also affect the team's performance such as player fitness, how the coach can change the atmosphere between players, and giving instructions during time outs.
